  "title": "Principal Consultant",
  "description": "<ul><li>Must have hands on experience in Designing, implementing and maintaining CI/CD pipelines to automate build, test, and deployment processes for Temenos banking software solutions.</li><li>Proficient in installing and configuring Temenos products and application servers like weblogic, websphere and its related components, ensuring seamless deployment and optimal performance.</li><li>Automate batch scheduling and integrations via Control-M/Autosys, Unix shell scripting, and SQL across upstream/downstream systems.</li><li>Collaborate with run, release, and vendor teams to ensure high availability, performance tuning, and ITIL-compliant change governance.</li><li>Provide L2/L3 production support, performing incident management, RCA, and permanent fixes for mission-critical banking systems</li></ul>",
